com.codecool.shop.model

Class LineItem

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.codecool.shop.model.LineItem

  • public class LineItem
extends java.lang.Object

    This class is used to construct LineItems stored in the shopping cart, and related methods

    The constructed objects each stores a Product object, and have quantity attribute to indicate the number of products it stores
    Since:
    2017-05-20
    Version:
    1.0
    Author:
    Majoross Daniel, Racz Anna, Adam Kovacs

    • Constructor Detail

      • LineItem

        public LineItem(Product product,
                int quantity)
        Constructor for the LineItem, it takes in a Product object and a quantity. It sets the LineItem's id as the same as the product it contains, calculates subtotal price.
        Parameters:
        product - The Product object to be contained by the LineItem.
        quantity - The number of the same item contained by the LineItem.

      • LineItem

        public LineItem(int id,
                Product product,
                int quantity)
        Constructor for the LineItem, it takes in an id a Product object and a quantity. It sets the LineItem's id and calculates subtotal price.
        Parameters:
        id - The id of the object. Needed mostly for constructing an Item from the database.
        product - The Product object to be contained by the LineItem.
        quantity - The number of the same item contained by the LineItem.
